---
title: Hoisin Beef and Mixed Veg Stir-Fry with Egg Noodles and Sesame Seeds
description: This Hoisin Beef and Mixed Veg Stir-Fry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
